commit.message:
sfp-machine.h (__FP_FRAC_SUB_4): Change operand constraint of y0 to "g".

	* config/i386/32/sfp-machine.h (__FP_FRAC_SUB_4): Change operand
	constraint of y0 to "g".

From-SVN: r152594
